## üîí Security Best Practices

### Environment Variables
- ‚úÖ Service role key ko `.env` file mein hi rakhein
- ‚úÖ `.env` file ko `.gitignore` mein add karein
- ‚ùå Kabhi bhi keys ko public repository mein push na karein

### RLS Policies
- ‚úÖ Production mein strict RLS policies use karein
- ‚úÖ Each table ke liye proper access control set karein
- ‚ùå `USING (true)` policy long-term mein use na karein

### Storage Buckets
- ‚úÖ Private data ke liye private buckets use karein
- ‚úÖ Public data (logos) ke liye hi public buckets use karein
- ‚úÖ File size limits set karein

### API Keys
- ‚úÖ Frontend mein sirf `anon` key use karein
- ‚úÖ Backend mein sirf `service_role` key use karein
- ‚úÖ Keys ko regularly rotate karein

